stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Idle
  Idle --> Listening: push-to-talk or typing
  Listening --> Provisional: stable query prefix
  Provisional --> Escalate: critical red flag
  Provisional --> Clarify: blocking slot missing
  Provisional --> StableCard: confidence threshold met
  Provisional --> Ambiguous: top candidates too close
  Ambiguous --> StableCard: pharmacist selects or more input arrives
  StableCard --> Frozen: pharmacist freezes/selects
  StableCard --> Refining: optional LLM request
  Refining --> StableCard: valid current-sequence refinement
  Refining --> StableCard: timeout/error; retain local card
  Refining --> Dropped: stale sequence
  Frozen --> Frozen: transcript changes ignored for main card
  Frozen --> Listening: unfreeze or clear
  Escalate --> Frozen: pharmacist acknowledges
  Clarify --> Listening: answer to next question
  Dropped --> Listening
  Listening --> Idle: clear/session end
